ed on tile coordinates, and one based on a bounding box. Classes that implement this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"protocol must implement one, and only one of the methods. Methods on this protocol will not be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"called on main thread, they will be called on the caller’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"requestQueue"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesourcedatasource","title":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOptionMinimumZoomLevel":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionMinimumZoomLevel","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionMinimumZoomLevel","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionMinimumZoomLevel"}],"abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSNumber","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" object containing an integer; specifies the minimum zoom level at","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"which to create vector tiles. The default value is 0.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionminimumzoomlevel"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer","title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSNumber","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" object containing an integer; specifies the size of the tile","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"buffer on each side. A value of 0 produces no buffer. A value of 512 produces a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"buffer as wide as the tile itself. Larger values produce fewer rendering","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"artifacts near tile edges and slower performance. The default value is 128.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionbuffer","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSource":{"role":"symbol","title":"MLNComputedShapeSource","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesource","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNComputedShapeSource","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"one tile at a time, to be shown on the map on demand. You implement a class"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conforming to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol that returns"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instances of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":", then add a computed shape source to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},{"type":"text","text":" object along with an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the computed shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSource/initWithIdentifier:dataSource:options:":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Returns a custom shape data source initialized with an identifier, data source, and a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"dictionary of options for the source according to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"style","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"specification","type":"text"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"title":"initWithIdentifier:dataSource:options:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesource\/initwithidentifier:datasource:options:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithIdentifier:dataSource:options:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource\/initWithIdentifier:dataSource:options:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithIdentifier:dataSource:options:"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOptionWrapsCoordinates":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionWrapsCoordinates","role":"symbol","title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionWrapsCoordinates","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionWrapsCoordinates"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"co